q1: To pass the correct number along that you received in the game.

There are 3 players, P1, P2 and P3.  Player one (P1) is shown a board of 144 cards facing downwards. Each card has a number on the card between 1-30 with various frequencies i.e some numbers appear more than one.   P1 selects a card, views the number and reports the hidden number to P2 .  P2 then has to report the hidden number that they have been told by P1 to P3.  P1 and P3 have no communication. It is now P3's job to report what the hidden number is..
